/AGENTS.md
/CONTEXT.md
/GEMINI.md
/WORKING.md
/memory/

# Internal strategy / architecture / design notes — NEVER commit.
# Public repo; this content includes risk-model and operational detail
# that should not be visible to adversaries or random readers.
# Anchored to repo root with a leading slash so it does NOT match
# docs/ARCHITECTURE.md (the existing operational scraper-architecture
# doc, which is fine to publish).
/ARCHITECTURE.md
/GITHUB-ACTIONS-SETUP.md
/MISTAKES.md
/PARSER-ARCHITECTURE.md
/STYLEGUIDE.md
/RISKS.md
/RUNBOOK.md
